WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.126
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.126 --> 00:00:03.080
I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:11.543
I have some things I want to talk to you about, but first of all, I just want to say thank you for all the likes, the subscribes, and the comments.

00:00:11.543 --> 00:00:19.245
It's a true blessing to us, and we just want to say thank you for supporting this YouTube channel as you have.

00:00:19.245 --> 00:00:20.386
God bless you all.

00:00:20.386 --> 00:00:32.386
I pray for you daily that the Lord increases you in every area of your life—physically, spiritually, financially, emotionally, everything—that the Lord will give you abundant overflow in your homes.

00:00:32.653 --> 00:00:40.595
I just want to say thank you from the bottom of our hearts for supporting this YouTube channel, and I appreciate your prayers for my family.

00:00:40.595 --> 00:00:42.479
I appreciate all your prayers.

00:00:42.859 --> 00:00:53.599
I'm going to do a video that I've already done before, but I felt because of the time that's passed since I made the video that I could do it better.

00:00:54.239 --> 00:00:59.111
I listened back to it and I thought, 'I think I can do better at that.

00:00:59.111 --> 00:01:01.280
' So, let's give it a shot.

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:11.280
I've told you before how the Lord took me out of my body and I shot up into outer space.

00:01:12.360 --> 00:01:24.851
I could see the Lord, though from His midway up, I could not see anything during the whole visitation.

00:01:27.380 --> 00:01:38.959
I don't know if it was God the Father or Jesus, but I'm going to tell you, we were in outer space and I could see the planets.

00:01:39.509 --> 00:01:42.252
It was like everything was shrunk down.

00:01:42.252 --> 00:01:49.565
I know they're millions of miles apart, but everything in the solar system seemed so small to us.

00:01:50.030 --> 00:01:55.875
We were looking at it like the planets were right there.

00:01:56.545 --> 00:02:02.209
I could see Saturn, Jupiter, and Mars.

00:02:02.209 --> 00:02:08.564
I could see it all, but we were standing right next to the Sun the whole time.

00:02:09.013 --> 00:02:13.764
The Sun was massive, and it was over to my right.

00:02:14.066 --> 00:02:21.248
The Lord was also to the right, and I was looking out at the Sun when He spoke to me.

00:02:21.632 --> 00:02:29.213
He said, 'Brandon, how long does it take for the Sun's light to get to the Earth?

00:02:29.213 --> 00:02:30.920
' I knew the answer.

00:02:31.160 --> 00:02:35.239
I said, 'It takes like eight minutes and 20 some seconds.

00:02:35.239 --> 00:02:40.987
' Right then, I knew the answer, but now I've probably butchered it.

00:02:41.907 --> 00:02:58.405
I told the Lord that at 186,000 miles per second, the light travels from the Sun and takes 8 minutes and 27 seconds to get to the Earth.

00:03:01.275 --> 00:03:07.094
He asked me, 'Brandon, what is faster than the speed of light?

00:03:07.094 --> 00:03:11.239
' I said, 'I don't know, Lord.

00:03:11.239 --> 00:03:14.263
' He said, 'The speed of thought.

00:03:14.263 --> 00:03:24.379
' He said, 'Brandon, whenever you die and you come to be with Me, you will travel at the speed of thought, not at the speed of light.

00:03:24.379 --> 00:03:40.924
' The speed of thought is actually way faster than the speed of light because you are there instantly instead of traveling at 186,000 miles per second.

00:03:43.111 --> 00:03:53.160
He was telling me all this, and then He talked to me about how far the nearest star is, which is light-years away.

00:03:53.160 --> 00:04:05.149
I don't remember exactly how far it was, but He told me it would take thousands of years to get there even at 186,000 miles per second.

00:04:10.608 --> 00:04:15.408
Then He said, 'I want to take you and show you something.

00:04:15.408 --> 00:04:20.667
' All of a sudden, we were instantaneously there.

00:04:21.140 --> 00:04:24.839
This is where it gets good.

00:04:26.640 --> 00:04:35.840
What I could see before me when we went into this room was a massive white room.

00:04:36.223 --> 00:04:41.591
There was no beginning and no end to this room.

00:04:48.577 --> 00:04:51.176
The light in the room was so piercing, but there was no ceiling, no floor, nothing.

00:04:57.450 --> 00:05:02.783
It was like a dimension in itself.

00:05:03.486 --> 00:05:07.505
There before me was the universe.

00:05:08.515 --> 00:05:13.440
This is heavy, but I'm telling you all it's fact.

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:18.205
The universe was in its own dimension.

00:05:18.205 --> 00:05:33.699
He created a room for the universe; all the galaxies were inside of another dimension that was endless.

00:05:34.699 --> 00:05:44.897
Before me, the universe was moving at the speed of light, being created.

00:05:44.897 --> 00:06:06.534
I could see inside of this massive area; it looked like cauliflower clouds—like thunderclouds moving very slowly—but it was forming right in front of my face.

00:06:06.534 --> 00:06:14.832
Stars were forming inside of this dimension, shrunk down.

00:06:14.832 --> 00:06:26.504
Though moving at 186,000 miles per second, it looked slow because He controls time.

00:06:26.504 --> 00:06:33.179
He is in control of all time; time does not exist around Him.

00:06:33.639 --> 00:06:48.484
At 186,000 miles per second, creating right before my eyes, it was moving so slowly.

00:07:06.755 --> 00:07:07.360
I could see how big it was since the beginning when He spoke it into existence, 'Let there be light.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:12.685
' All the things He said in Genesis were moving.

00:07:38.025 --> 00:07:38.520
It was the size of a Volkswagen Beetle—I don't know why, but that's the way it stood out to me.

00:07:57.210 --> 00:07:57.465
It was that shape and it was moving in all directions—downward, upward, left, right, north, south, east, west—all at the same time, creating from the center.

00:07:58.980 --> 00:08:11.359
It was like a thunderstorm, moving slowly like thunderclouds, all being formed and created inside of this room.

00:08:11.359 --> 00:08:15.830
Stars were moving and being created from every direction.

00:08:18.399 --> 00:08:18.759
It was all moving equally.

00:08:21.639 --> 00:08:34.599
He spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, you know in My Word where it says I can measure the span of the universe in My hand?

00:08:34.599 --> 00:08:39.440
' He said, 'I'm going to show you how I do it.

00:08:39.440 --> 00:08:47.886
' He took that universe and shrunk it down right before my eyes.

00:08:47.886 --> 00:08:52.196
He said, 'I create and I am able to manipulate it.

00:08:52.196 --> 00:08:57.410
' It was like clay before Him.

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:11.704
He said, 'Brandon, it is in a dimension in itself,' and He could stretch it out or shrink it.

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:27.566
He put it in His hand, and He had the whole universe—billions and billions of galaxies—shrunk down in this dimension.

00:09:27.566 --> 00:09:32.668
He said, 'Look, I can step into it.

00:09:32.668 --> 00:09:49.748
' He stretched it out and said, 'I can step into it or I can shrink it down, but Brandon, I measure it all in My hand.

00:09:49.748 --> 00:10:01.732
' He put it in His hand—it was stretched out and he showed it to me like a cube—and it was still growing.

00:10:03.776 --> 00:10:06.116
It never stopped; stars were still forming in His hand as He was holding it.

00:10:06.116 --> 00:10:11.380
No matter how He stretched it or shrank it, it was still being created.

00:10:11.380 --> 00:10:15.880
I just stood there and watched.

00:10:15.880 --> 00:10:24.160
I know I wasn't in my body; this was more than just a dream.

00:10:24.160 --> 00:10:28.164
This happened to me over 20 years ago and I've never forgotten it.

00:10:28.164 --> 00:10:34.000
I remember every detail like it was yesterday, other than the numbers.

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:39.269
I've told you I've overcome my learning disabilities.

00:10:39.269 --> 00:10:49.514
He took me then and said, 'I want to show you something else,' and He showed me Heaven.

00:10:49.514 --> 00:10:57.280
Heaven was a massive planet, about the size of three Jupiters.

00:10:57.280 --> 00:11:03.458
Heaven is a massive planet, like a dimension in itself.

00:11:11.947 --> 00:11:12.253
I could see the gold; it was pure light.

00:11:14.613 --> 00:11:22.024
It was beyond comprehension; I cannot give it adequate justice with words.

00:11:48.268 --> 00:11:55.113
It was inside its own dimension.

00:11:58.080 --> 00:12:01.940
The universe was on the edge of Heaven.

00:12:01.940 --> 00:12:11.173
We were standing out there again, and I was looking at all the walls.

00:12:11.173 --> 00:12:26.820
There are massive walls all around Heaven, and I could see buildings—all kinds of houses and buildings.

00:12:26.820 --> 00:12:32.954
It's like a major city, but beautiful beyond words.

00:12:39.725 --> 00:12:42.459
I could see the walls formed with gold and all kinds of beautiful stones.

00:12:42.459 --> 00:12:57.590
Then all of a sudden I looked up, and the sky above me was filled with beautiful pinks, purples, and whites, swirled like a paisley print.

00:13:09.280 --> 00:13:09.624
He said, 'Brandon, this is My portion; I set this aside for Myself, Heaven.

00:13:09.624 --> 00:13:14.200
But son, I'm giving you the universe.

00:13:26.399 --> 00:13:26.959
All the galaxies are going to be yours.

00:13:26.959 --> 00:13:38.589
' He said that is the portion He is giving to His kids, the born-again believers.

00:13:38.589 --> 00:14:04.013
When you come home to be with Me after the thousand-year reign, you will spend eternity traveling at the speed of thought throughout all the galaxies and universes, going from one to another.

00:14:04.013 --> 00:14:18.284
There are planets and stars being made, and you will rule and reign forever and ever with Me over eternity in those places.

00:14:18.284 --> 00:14:25.240
Why people say, 'Why would I want my own galaxy?

00:14:25.240 --> 00:14:28.475
' I don't know.

00:14:28.475 --> 00:14:39.792
We have a mansion in Heaven, but I'm trying to tell you what I saw.

00:14:39.792 --> 00:14:48.691
Then He said to me, 'Do you see all that?

00:14:48.691 --> 00:14:57.130
' And I could see the stars being formed before me.

00:15:06.360 --> 00:15:07.142
That dimension was still being spread out, but He had opened it up and we were inside of it now.

00:15:07.142 --> 00:15:15.640
Heaven was on the edge of it, and the universe and all the galaxies were on this side.

00:15:29.100 --> 00:15:29.410
He told me, 'You will rule and reign with Me forever and ever.

00:15:29.410 --> 00:15:32.440
' You're never going to get bored.

00:15:32.440 --> 00:15:48.145
You'll travel at the speed of thought to all your brothers and sisters; the whole body of Christ is going to be ruling and reigning.

00:16:04.818 --> 00:16:07.787
He's creating a new Heaven and a new Earth.

00:16:11.009 --> 00:16:13.068
Folks, we have an amazing future.

00:16:13.068 --> 00:16:17.600
God has an amazing plan for His church and His people.

00:16:17.600 --> 00:16:22.252
It is not for us to be down and out.

00:16:22.252 --> 00:16:26.639
We're going to rule and reign with Him for all eternity.

00:16:36.288 --> 00:16:42.818
The Lord told me, 'Brandon, I am a big, big God.

00:16:45.545 --> 00:16:55.140
I want you to go back and tell My people they think way too small.

00:16:57.973 --> 00:17:12.980
I want them to start believing Me for bigger, for I am a big God able to do exceedingly abundantly above all they dare ask or think.

00:17:12.980 --> 00:17:14.564
' Remember that.

00:17:14.564 --> 00:17:18.925
He has it all in His hand.

00:17:28.039 --> 00:17:29.560
There are more stars than there are grains of sand on our beaches.

00:17:31.080 --> 00:17:38.653
You'll never be able to wrap your mind around how big the universe is.

00:17:38.653 --> 00:17:43.773
It's basically endless, but He's able to control it.

00:17:45.771 --> 00:17:50.200
It's still being created because life is still being created.

00:17:55.880 --> 00:18:01.290
People are getting born again every single day, and He has a place assigned just for you.

00:18:07.047 --> 00:18:15.631
One day, when we rule and reign with Him, whatever that purpose is, I have no idea.

00:18:15.631 --> 00:18:19.773
All I know is there's a big plan for us, and He loves you.

00:18:23.050 --> 00:18:25.799
I know that when we get there, He'll have a galaxy for you.

00:18:32.890 --> 00:18:40.040
The Milky Way is the galaxy we're in, but there are billions more.

00:18:42.058 --> 00:18:52.342
I hope I didn't butcher that, but I tried my best to explain something so amazing and life-changing.

00:18:54.457 --> 00:19:00.015
He wanted me to tell you how big He really is and that He's endless.

00:19:00.834 --> 00:19:03.205
Nothing is too hard for Him.

00:19:03.679 --> 00:19:06.216
All things are possible to him who believes.

00:19:06.216 --> 00:19:08.613
You just have to believe with simple faith.

00:19:08.613 --> 00:19:15.455
If you have the faith of a mustard seed, He said you would move a mountain.

00:19:23.015 --> 00:19:23.207
If you do not doubt in your heart, you'll have whatsoever things you say—Mark 11:24.

00:19:28.629 --> 00:19:37.084
I'm believing with all my heart for big things in 2024 and 2025.

00:19:40.662 --> 00:19:44.880
It's time to believe God for the impossible today.

00:19:48.560 --> 00:19:54.380
He's no respecter of persons, and what God did for one, He'll do for another.

00:19:54.380 --> 00:19:57.640
God loves you and He has an amazing plan.

00:19:57.640 --> 00:20:02.120
Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:20:02.120 --> 00:20:02.907
Think about that.

00:20:02.907 --> 00:20:07.440
He wants you to be in health; He wants you to be above and not beneath.

00:20:09.679 --> 00:20:12.133
He wants you to have a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:20:13.420 --> 00:20:22.414
We are the salt of the earth, ministering to our neighbors and telling them that Jesus loves them and is coming soon.

00:20:25.497 --> 00:20:30.365
Jesus is coming soon, folks.

00:20:31.142 --> 00:20:32.586
I hope you're ready.

00:20:32.586 --> 00:20:34.234
I hope your heart is prepared.

00:20:39.840 --> 00:20:42.130
A lot of people say, 'I don't believe in the Rapture.

00:20:42.130 --> 00:20:43.580
' That's your problem.

00:20:43.580 --> 00:20:53.920
I do, and He's coming back for you and me and those who believe and are seeking Him daily.

00:20:59.572 --> 00:21:00.632
Let me pray for you.

00:21:02.950 --> 00:21:04.910
Father, I thank You for 'big.

00:21:04.910 --> 00:21:10.200
' I thank You, God, for 'huge.

00:21:10.200 --> 00:21:24.120
' I thank You for 'ginormous'—that You are an awesome God able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that we'd ask or think.

00:21:24.120 --> 00:21:36.863
I thank You, God, that You're creating something amazing for me, my children, my wife, and all my friends and family.

00:21:41.820 --> 00:21:44.720
You have eternity; time is endless with You.

00:21:45.340 --> 00:21:51.106
You have everything in the span of Your hand.

00:21:51.106 --> 00:22:04.840
Father, I thank You that You come and visit me, that You have a plan for my life, and that You love me enough to show me secret things and things to come—for us to believe You for bigger, not smaller.

00:22:05.320 --> 00:22:08.820
We get out of our stinking thinking, poverty, and lack.

00:22:08.820 --> 00:22:11.260
Father, You're a God of more than enough.

00:22:11.260 --> 00:22:14.680
I've seen the edges of Heaven; there's no poverty in Heaven.

00:22:17.471 --> 00:22:27.132
There's only abundance, overflow of gold, rubies, sapphires, diamonds, pearls, and beautiful gemstones beyond comprehension.

00:22:36.753 --> 00:22:46.800
I thank You, Father, that You've created this for us and that You love us enough not to give us some shack down by the river, but to give us a mansion.

00:22:46.800 --> 00:22:53.874
You said You'd give us our heart's desires, God, and I thank You for that.

00:22:55.840 --> 00:22:59.826
You said, 'Beloved, I wish there would be on earth as it is in heaven.

00:22:59.826 --> 00:23:10.380
' I thank You, Father, that we don't have to struggle on this earth; we can have more than enough.

00:23:16.680 --> 00:23:19.874
Lord, we give You glory, honor, and praise.

00:23:19.874 --> 00:23:30.440
We call every single person watching this video healed, whole, and well, delivered from oppression.

00:23:30.760 --> 00:23:37.250
Strongholds are broken off their lives, set free by the blood of the Lamb and the word of their testimony.

00:23:37.250 --> 00:23:47.811
We thank You, Lord, that marriages are restored, homes are good, and children are blessed.

00:23:53.874 --> 00:23:54.189
Father, I thank You for a great year in 2024.

00:24:04.560 --> 00:24:12.080
By the time we get to the end of 2024, we will say, 'Look what the Lord has done.

00:24:12.080 --> 00:24:14.750
' Great is Your faithfulness to me.

00:24:16.206 --> 00:24:29.240
All my life You have been faithful and so, so good.

00:24:32.622 --> 00:24:33.856
Thank You, Father.

00:24:42.284 --> 00:24:48.034
I will sing and give You praise for Your goodness today.

00:25:00.039 --> 00:25:00.580
Thank You that we're healed and whole.

00:25:11.320 --> 00:25:13.880
I bless You, Lord.

00:25:13.880 --> 00:25:20.880
I just want to say thank you all for watching and supporting us.

00:25:21.520 --> 00:25:28.680
I hope this video blessed you and inspires you to believe for bigger.

00:25:30.440 --> 00:25:34.840
Jesus loves you so much and has great plans ahead for you.

00:25:49.080 --> 00:25:52.710
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:25:52.710 --> 00:25:55.746
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you.

00:25:56.039 --> 00:25:57.799
We will see you next time.

00:25:58.502 --> 00:26:02.017
Have a blessed day.

00:26:02.017 --> 00:26:02.720
Bye-bye.
